Package cz.cuni.mff.kocur.considerations

Package that contains all the considerations our agents use.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConsiderActive
    This decision considers if BaseInterest is active.
    Consideration
    Abstract class that represents a basic Consideration.
    ConsiderCooldown
    Considers cooldown of the ability that is obtained from target using getAbility().
    ConsiderCreepHealth
    Considers creep's health in relation to hero's damage.
    ConsiderDistanceToTarget
    Considers distance to target.
    ConsiderGameTime
    Considers game time.
    ConsiderGoldYield
    Consideration that normalizes the maximum gold yield of BaseEntity to range given by PARAM_RANGE_MIN and PARAM_RANGE_MAX.
    ConsiderInventorySpace
    Consideration that considers space in the inventory.
    ConsiderItemPresent
    Consideration that considers if an item is present inside the inventory.
    ConsiderMoney
    Consideration that considers agent's money and item's price.
    ConsiderProjectileSpeed
    Class that represents a consideration, that aims at considering speed of the hero's projectiles.
    ConsiderSecretShop
    Consideration that considers, if the target shop is a secret shop.
    ConsiderSourceHealth
    Consideration that considers the source's health.
    ConsiderSourceMana
    Consideration that considers source's mana.
    ConsiderTargetHealth
    Consideration that considers target's health.
    ConsiderTargetValue
    Consideration that considers target's value.
    ConsiderThreat
    Consideration that considers threat from target's value field.
    ConsiderTimePassed
    Consideration that considers time, that has passed from the last time the decision was executed.
